Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.36,0:01:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.18,0:01:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来，请好好欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲜血淋漓的表演时间开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.14,0:01:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这废物！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.20,0:01:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔用不留情面的一击打倒了弗罗斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.06,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.12,0:02:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，针对接下来的比赛，制订了新的规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.14,0:02:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在刚才，新的立体屏障建好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,选手要是碰到它，就算是在空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也会被当作出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手的下一个对手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,金属人马盖特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坚固的躯体和变化多端的攻击把贝吉塔逼到困境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔变身超级赛亚人，想要扭转局势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.96,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然，身体出现了不明原因的不良反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,热量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.54,0:03:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「意外的艰苦战斗！贝吉塔愤怒的大爆炸！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.04,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.14,0:03:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手突然不动了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.98,0:03:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙确实是在散发热量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是还有什么其他的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕大人，您的笑声真粗俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.80,0:04:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用你管！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.74,0:04:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很可疑啊，象帕那令人反胃的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就和他偷吃了我珍藏的牛排时的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔！你快下来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么意思？老孙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔先生现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法充分呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.84,0:04:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那个屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个屏障内部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空气非常稀薄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.38,0:04:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然！都怪那家伙制定的古怪规则！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.22,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕！你们在那个屏障上动了手脚吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别胡说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们并没有在屏障上动手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不可能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好看看下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特地设计成了竞技场里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以自由流通空气的结构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，马盖特的燃烧能力太强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空气消耗的量超过了流通的量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们也同意了比赛规则的更改啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去会先败下阵来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闭嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.96,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不需要你的建议！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.44,0:05:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之，快点分出胜负就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是开口说话，呼吸都会变得更困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，贝吉塔怎么就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不听孙君的话呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.22,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去贝吉塔会输的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要输啊，爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手，放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战斗的时候，像我一样灵活变通是很必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊呀，马盖特选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.68,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再次用熔岩口水瞄准贝吉塔选手发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烫烫烫烫…好烫…好烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然头顶是空档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？只是滚烫的水蒸气吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我停下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，贝吉塔选手勉强躲开了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是挺顽强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.72,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.02,0:07:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判！刚刚的攻击不是违反规则了吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.02,0:07:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马盖特选手只是引燃了他放的屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才爆炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不是武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,简直是在愚弄我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些家伙该不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,买通了裁判吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有的事，比鲁斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判的判定是非常公平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，金属人的打法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很好玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是我，该怎么战斗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,近战时的普通攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对那铜墙铁壁般的身体毫无作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.74,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在炎热和缺氧不断消耗体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪怕先找到对付口水的方法也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.82,0:08:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是背后有屏障，限制了行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样一来，即使是贝吉塔那么强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也可能会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔！输了的话我可不会饶了你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些家伙都在随随便便自说自话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我这招彻底干掉你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个动作是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.90,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，贝吉塔选手积蓄了惊人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烫！烫烫烫烫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一边的马盖特选手也进一步提高了温度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好热！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然在这里都能感受到热量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那里面的温度一定高得像地狱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.02,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.10,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没用的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔，快闪开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可…可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.14,0:10:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,输掉了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会吧，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有出界！没有出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁…裁判！怎么可能没有出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是完全落到场外去了吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手的落地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.52,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是擂台的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以判定为仍然站在擂台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不是在场外！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了！得救了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判，判得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的，是谁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪个混蛋请了这么个不靠谱的裁判！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是象帕大人您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.42,0:12:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕那家伙看上去很懊恼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔这次是多亏了规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然大家都很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是贝吉塔先生是怎么想的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.48,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我居然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本大爷我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然被规则救了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下可糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂，你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.56,0:13:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要不碰到那个屏障就可以了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是第7宇宙的赛亚人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙，是白痴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一生气就失去控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真难看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又蠢又丢人的是象帕大人您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是比鲁斯大人认可的宇宙第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不为所动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.92,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是多么强大的力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说，芭朵斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干嘛不造个不会被弄坏的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋，那种东西随便做做就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是象帕大人您自己说的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能充分呼吸，我就能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.46,0:16:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好哦！把你的怒火全部发出来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那招是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这种地方，你来真的吗？贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闪光！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还差一点就出界了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就那样压下去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就结束了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这堆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,破铜烂铁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马盖特选手出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手获胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.62,0:19:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸，好帅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连马盖特都输了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本该把屏障做得牢固一点的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啰…啰嗦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,双方都表现得很好，是一场精彩的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.78,0:19:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来竞技场必须得重建了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干得不错，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然把竞技场都破坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟是那么坚固的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,按常理出牌赢不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实根本没必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做到那种程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦，那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才一直都那么强的，怎么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是被贝吉塔先生最后那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.32,0:20:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「破铜烂铁」伤到了心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马盖特他们那些金属人心灵很脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要稍微被骂几句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就会失去战斗的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,维斯！这么重要的事，你怎么不早说!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.86,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人，这种事情一早知道就没意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来，贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.22,0:21:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要是认真打，其实能赢得更快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.76,0:21:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗，果然你也注意到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来该我了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别了亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.37,0:21:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红的天空下的我和你　我站在你右边　而你待在我的左边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.46,0:22:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「我很喜欢你　这一生都不会忘记你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.96,0:22:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想说出口　又咽了回去　不如还是　把话埋在心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.34,0:22:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然两人被困在　一场滂沱落花雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.56,0:22:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,簌簌的　谱成一首动人旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.65,0:22:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少把你的身影　从我的眼前隐去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.03,0:22:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.28,0:22:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.76,0:22:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！我是悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.74,0:22:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的赛亚人虽然看起来和我们不太一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.06,0:22:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是不愧同为战斗民族，加贝很厉害嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.68,0:22:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔，你忘记规则了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.28,0:22:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道你变回从前的自己了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下集『龙珠超』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.86,0:23:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「不要忘记赛亚人的骄傲！贝吉塔VS第6宇宙赛亚人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.96,0:23:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要看啊！

